

	 
      ~~~~~  Roses  ~~~~~    Roses for Ari of purest snow white  sealed with a kiss from blood-tainted lips.  Dipped in the sin of a hidden past  coated in honey from bees that don't sting.  Left for her there to wither and die.  but preserved by the hope of unspoken lies.  Yet all that she sees and all that she will  are roses for Ari of soft snow white silk.  ~fin~ 
    
